@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state Idle
Idle : entry/To action
Idle : do/Remain in same state
Idle : exit/Login / Register

state Register
Register : entry/Register
Register : do/Register after validating
Register : exit/Login/Invalid registration

state InvalidRegistration
InvalidRegistration : entry/Invalid registration
InvalidRegistration : do/Cannot register
InvalidRegistration : exit/Abnormal termination

state Login
Login : entry/Login
Login : do/Login using valid username and password
Login : exit/Invalid login/To home page

state InvalidLogin
InvalidLogin : entry/Invalid login
InvalidLogin : do/Cannot login
InvalidLogin : exit/Abnormal termination

state CheckWeather
CheckWeather : entry/Home page
CheckWeather : do/Check weather for current or another location
CheckWeather : exit/Idle

CheckWeather --> WeatherInfo
CheckWeather --> InvalidLocation

state WeatherInfo
WeatherInfo : entry/View weather info
WeatherInfo : do/Update and show selected weather information to the user
WeatherInfo : exit/Additional details

state AdditionalDetails
AdditionalDetails : entry/View additional weather details
AdditionalDetails : do/View alerts, a weekly analysis, a future prediction, or a graph
AdditionalDetails : exit/Idle

state Logout
Logout : entry/End session
Logout : do/Log out
Logout : exit/Idle
@enduml
